Super Freaks 1 Ultimate Edition 3.0 is here to celebrate the 1st anniversary!!!
Play the new Uncle Swordsman Story and rocket around at insane speeds with your aura. Take down Kranion and Sticky's dad Marrow Prime and other new bosses in the craziest, biggest update yet!
